                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-206-victim1703 t18300916-206-viclabel1048"></join>. On the 3rd of August I went to my shop in the court-yard adjoining my house at <placeName id="t18300916-206-crimeloc1049">Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-206-crimeloc1049" type="placeName" value="Islington"></interp>
