            ; I have seen all the property since, and can swear to all my own tools - the prisoner has worked for me.</p>
               <p>CHARLES FEAR. I am <rs id="t18300916-206-viclabel1050" type="occupation">apprentice</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-206-victim1706 t18300916-206-viclabel1050"></join> to the prosecutor. On the 3rd of August I lost a great many tools; these are them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-206-person1709">
                  JOSEPH 
                  MELLISH
               <interp inst="t18300916-206-person1709" type="surname" value="MELLISH"></interp>
